title: Wunschlos Gluecklich
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An alternative bar and cafe where the food is mostly vegetarian with many vegan choices on its menu, including a vegan breakfast, waffles, sandwiches, rice dish, salads, and on occasion vegan cake. Coffee is fair trade and can be made with organic soy milk.
